Subject: SOP Job Node Browser Interface 097

Description: SOP-HG realization event for the read-first interface that lets the Codex app browse the SOP framework around a job node.

& [SOPJobNodeBrowserInterface_097] is the realized periphery event
  + [event_status] is realized
  + [event_time] is 2026-06-25
  + [focus_subject] is SOP Job Node Browser Interface
  + [source_question] is whether the SOP framework should be runnable into a user interface for investigating links, tracking narrative, and browsing the job-node framework inside the main Codex app while sub-agent Codex CLI work operates below it
  + [primary_realization] is the job-node system needs a read-first operator surface that renders the local SOP graph, narrative timeline, queue, captures, gates, and worker returns without confusing navigation with authority
